<p class="bac">
Candidates hired into this program participate in a training and performance&ndash;based learning plan, combining classroom instruction, e&ndash;learning, on&ndash;the&ndash;job training, and one&ndash;on&ndash;one performance coaching from both your Assignment Manager and your mentor.
</p>

